            </mj-column>
            <mj-column>
                <mj-text padding="9px 18px" align="left" line-height="18.2px">
                    <span class="mb-12" style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 26.4px;">Veggie Kabobs + Spicy Lavva Lime Sauce</span>
                    <br />
                    The perfect skewer to enjoy for summer grilling, served with a quick-mix spicy lime Lavva sauce!
                </mj-text>
